<?xml version='1.0' encoding='UTF-8'?><?xml-stylesheet href="http://www.blogger.com/styles/atom.css" type="text/css"?><feed xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom' xmlns:openSearch='http://a9.com/-/spec/opensearchrss/1.0/' xmlns:georss='http://www.georss.org/georss'><id>tag:blogger.com,1999:blog-4282025301274571566</id><updated>2009-07-21T14:15:00.246-07:00</updated><title type='text'>Eboshi</title><subtitle type='html'></subtitle><link rel='http://schemas.google.com/g/2005#feed' type='application/atom+xml' href='http://eboshi-app.blogspot.com/feeds/posts/default'/><link rel='self' type='application/atom+xml' href='http://www.blogger.com/feeds/4282025301274571566/posts/default'/><link rel='alternate' type='text/html' href='http://eboshi-app.blogspot.com/'/><author><name>Micah Geisel</name><uri>http://www.blogger.com/profile/17366493748194963864</uri><email>noreply@blogger.com</email></author><generator version='7.00' uri='http://www.blogger.com'>Blogger</generator><openSearch:totalResults>2</openSearch:totalResults><openSearch:startIndex>1</openSearch:startIndex><openSearch:itemsPerPage>25</openSearch:itemsPerPage><entry><id>tag:blogger.com,1999:blog-4282025301274571566.post-6995997114962325121</id><published>2009-07-21T14:15:00.000-07:00</published><updated>2009-07-21T14:15:00.316-07:00</updated><title type='text'>Bugfix: Works in Safari, Chrome!</title><content type='html'>Tracked down a nasty little bug that prevented Eboshi from working correctly in Safari and Chrome. If you have previously tried to use Eboshi in those browsers, try again! Firefox is still the only officially supported browser, though, so I recommend you use that.&lt;div class="blogger-post-footer"&gt;&lt;img width='1' height='1' src='https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/tracker/4282025301274571566-6995997114962325121?l=eboshi-app.blogspot.com'/&gt;&lt;/div&gt;</content><link rel='replies' type='application/atom+xml' href='http://eboshi-app.blogspot.com/feeds/6995997114962325121/comments/default' title='Post Comments'/><link rel='replies' type='text/html' href='http://eboshi-app.blogspot.com/2009/07/bugfix-works-in-safari-chrome.html#comment-form' title='0 Comments'/><link rel='edit' type='application/atom+xml' href='http://www.blogger.com/feeds/4282025301274571566/posts/default/6995997114962325121'/><link rel='self' type='application/atom+xml' href='http://www.blogger.com/feeds/4282025301274571566/posts/default/6995997114962325121'/><link rel='alternate' type='text/html' href='http://eboshi-app.blogspot.com/2009/07/bugfix-works-in-safari-chrome.html' title='Bugfix: Works in Safari, Chrome!'/><author><name>Micah Geisel</name><uri>http://www.blogger.com/profile/17366493748194963864</uri><email>noreply@blogger.com</email><gd:extendedProperty xmlns:gd='http://schemas.google.com/g/2005' name='OpenSocialUserId' value='10850278849644445499'/></author><thr:total xmlns:thr='http://purl.org/syndication/thread/1.0'>0</thr:total></entry><entry><id>tag:blogger.com,1999:blog-4282025301274571566.post-3235144445339792814</id><published>2009-07-14T16:09:00.000-07:00</published><updated>2009-07-14T16:18:34.738-07:00</updated><title type='text'>Feature: format your notes with Textile!</title><content type='html'>Hey kids! I figured I'd start a blog to increase communication between me, the developer, and y'all, the users.&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;Anyhow, first up is a new feature, requested by Chris Hackett, but improved, immeasurably, by your humble servant, myself... you can format your notes with Textile!&lt;br /&gt;&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;*bold* turns into &lt;span style="font-weight: bold;"&gt;bold&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;_italic&lt;span style="font-style: italic;"&gt;_&lt;/span&gt; turns into &lt;span style="font-style: italic;"&gt;italic&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;span style="font-style: italic;"&gt;&lt;/span&gt;line breaks actually show up on the invoice!&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;and oh so much more... [&lt;a href="http://www.textism.com/tools/textile/" target="_blank"&gt;here's a full reference&lt;/a&gt;]&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;Let me know what y'all think by commenting here, or emailing me.&lt;div class="blogger-post-footer"&gt;&lt;img width='1' height='1' src='https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/tracker/4282025301274571566-3235144445339792814?l=eboshi-app.blogspot.com'/&gt;&lt;/div&gt;</content><link rel='replies' type='application/atom+xml' href='http://eboshi-app.blogspot.com/feeds/3235144445339792814/comments/default' title='Post Comments'/><link rel='replies' type='text/html' href='http://eboshi-app.blogspot.com/2009/07/feature-format-your-notes-with-textile.html#comment-form' title='0 Comments'/><link rel='edit' type='application/atom+xml' href='http://www.blogger.com/feeds/4282025301274571566/posts/default/3235144445339792814'/><link rel='self' type='application/atom+xml' href='http://www.blogger.com/feeds/4282025301274571566/posts/default/3235144445339792814'/><link rel='alternate' type='text/html' href='http://eboshi-app.blogspot.com/2009/07/feature-format-your-notes-with-textile.html' title='Feature: format your notes with Textile!'/><author><name>Micah Geisel</name><uri>http://www.blogger.com/profile/17366493748194963864</uri><email>noreply@blogger.com</email><gd:extendedProperty xmlns:gd='http://schemas.google.com/g/2005' name='OpenSocialUserId' value='10850278849644445499'/></author><thr:total xmlns:thr='http://purl.org/syndication/thread/1.0'>0</thr:total></entry></feed>